text: Marina Zhukova (born 15 October 1966) is a Russian rower. She competed in the women's double sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tver
